    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Married women of mature years, usually with connotation of social rank, dignity, and propriety; often, but not ecessarily , associated with the mother of a large family.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
